➜海南省委原常委、海口市委原书记张琦受贿案一审被判无期徒刑
http://www.sohu.com/a/436033184_260616	32499
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
